response.overview: This assortment starts with a pair of long 1950s clips before focusing on the swinging 60s. In the opener a glamorous brunette lounges in her boudoir and then, in contrast, an active ponytailed gal enjoys, among other things, a heavy-duty vibrating exercise belt. Then the colorful 60s take over and offer up a titillating ensemble of blonde, brunette, bouffant, and redheaded talent posing at home and in the studio. Watch for an especially attractive blonde in a long color clip near the end!
response.title: Nudie Cuties: Volume 11
